# Specifications Tracking

- Use specifications.md as the source of truth for development
- Mark features as follows:
  - [ ] Unstarted feature
  - [~] In-progress feature
  - [x] Completed and tested feature
- All MVP features must be completed before starting "Further features"
- Add comment with date when marking features complete
- Include test coverage information when completing features
- Update README.md with completed feature documentation

## Testing Requirements
- Each completed feature requires:
  - Unit tests for core functionality
  - Integration tests for user flows
  - Manual verification on both iOS and Android
  - Cross-device testing on at least 2 screen sizes

## Documentation Standards
- Update README.md after each feature completion
- Include screenshots in README.md for UI features
- Document API integrations and data models
- Keep installation instructions current
